era-bootstrap-blog-template-768x622.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><br>As a metalhead, I am sure you&#8217;re pretty familiar with Pantera. Well, this is different. It&#8217;s a blog template based on Bootstrap and React that features five main demos and over forty UI elements.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>All the components perfectly harmonize, ensuring great operation out of the box. Note: You can fine-tune Pantera further.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Along with the extensive online documentation, you can also contact the professional support team. This is all part of the deal to speed up the development process and create a powerful blog.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"blog-btn\"><a class=\"preview_btn\" href=\"https:\/\/colorlib.com\/go\/pantera\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Download<\/a> <a class=\"cart_btn\" href=\"https:\/\/colorlib.com\/go\/pantera-demo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Preview<\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">10. Binduz<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1422\" src=\"https:\/\/adminlte.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/binduz-bootstrap-blog-template.jpg\" alt=\"binduz bootstrap blog template\" width=\"1200\" height=\"972\" srcset=\"https:\/\/adminlte.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/binduz-bootstrap-blog-template.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/adminlte.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/binduz-bootstrap-blog-template-300x243.jpg 300w, https:\/\/adminlte.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/binduz-bootstrap-blog-template-1024x829.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/adminlte.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/binduz-bootstrap-blog-template-768x622.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><br>Newspaper websites and blogs all become a reality with the quick-to-execute Binduz. Sure, you need basic coding knowledge, but that&#8217;s about it.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Binduz is easy to use and has heaps of ready-made material to do you well. For instance, you get twelve demos, four he